msgctxt "84_Customer Ready for Ramen"
msgid "I wonder what was up with that ramen shop guy?"
msgstr "¿Me pregunto qué le pasaba a ese tipo?"

msgctxt "96_Kiryu"
msgid "Excuse me. Did you see a guy pass by wearing a white uniform?"
msgstr "Disculpe. ¿Vio pasar a un hombre con un uniforme blanco?"

msgctxt "108_Customer Ready for Ramen"
msgid "Yeah, I just saw him come running out of the shop."
msgstr "Sí, lo acabo de ver salir corriendo de la tienda."

msgctxt "120_Customer Ready for Ramen"
msgid "He went to the end of this street and turned right. Is something wrong?"
msgstr "Fue hasta el final de esta calle y giró a la derecha. ¿Paso Algo?"

msgctxt "132_Kiryu"
msgid "No, nothing big. Thanks a lot."
msgstr "No, nada grave. Muchas gracias."

msgctxt "144_Kiryu"
msgid "(Matsuyama headed east on Taihei Boulevard. I better go after him.)"
msgstr "Matsuyama se dirigió al este por Boulevard Taihei. Será mejor que lo siga.)\""

